  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个TCP报文结构图，用于医疗科技团队培训。重点是展示标准TCP头部字段，同时在Data部分体现我们的业务场景——LabAnalyzer和EMR系统的数据同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TCP Packet",
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "Data",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。标准头部前160位是固定的，包括URG、ACK、SYN、FIN这些标志位，还有Window和Checksum。您说的LabAnalyzer和EMR_Sync是要放在Options字段还是直接替换Data区域？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Data",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "LabAnalyzer放在160-191位的Options区域，标注清楚来源；EMR_Sync放在192-255位的Data段，表示这是实际要同步的电子病历数据。这样学员能一眼看出业务数据在报文中的位置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "Data",
        "Options"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把结构搭好了：0-31位是Source Port和Destination Port，32-95位是Sequence和Acknowledgment Number，96-111位是控制标志位包括URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN，112-159位是Window、Checksum和Urgent Pointer。然后160-191位标注HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，192-255位是Data(HealthTech_EMR_Sync)。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "标志位的顺序对吗？URG是紧急指针有效位，ACK是确认号有效位，这个顺序和RFC 793一致吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一致。96-99位是Data Offset，100-105位Reserved保留，然后106位URG、107位ACK、108位PSH、109位RST、110位SYN、111位FIN，完全按照RFC规范。Window在112-127位，Urgent Pointer紧跟在Checksum后面144-159位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Window",
