      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "有个细节需要修正——Acknowledgment的拼写，你写的是Acknowledgment还是Acknowledgement？RFC里是Acknowledgment，没有中间的e。另外标题用\"TCP Packet\"就行，简洁一些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，Acknowledgment Number现在拼写正确，标题也简化为\"TCP Packet\"。最终结构：0-15 Source Port，16-31 Destination Port，32-63 Sequence Number，64-95 Acknowledgment Number，控制标志位106-111，112-127 Window，128-143 Checksum，144-159 Urgent Pointer，160-191 HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，192-255 Data(HealthTech_EMR_Sync)。",
